# Ragdoll Archers Website - Cloudflare Pages Redirects

# Domain redirects - www to root domain (IMPORTANT: must be first)
https://www.ragdollarchers.app/* https://ragdollarchers.app/:splat 301!
http://www.ragdollarchers.app/* https://ragdollarchers.app/:splat 301!

# Force HTTPS on root domain
http://ragdollarchers.app/* https://ragdollarchers.app/:splat 301!

# Game shortcuts - redirect to game section
/game /#game 301
/play /#game 301

# SEO-friendly redirects - alternative URLs
/strategy /guide 301
/walkthrough /guide 301
/weapons /arrows 301
/help /tips 301

# Old Google-indexed pages - redirect to homepage for SEO preservation
